                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18231203-69-off364 t18231203-69-cd365"></join>, eight sovereigns, a half sovereign, sixpence, and a 10 l. Bank note, the monies of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18231203-69-victim710" type="victimName">
                           James Serle 
